          <targetForm>fisiche</targetForm>
        </over_capitalisation></foreign_word> <foreign_word foreign_language="Italiano"><over_capitalisation>
          <originalForm>E</originalForm>

          <targetForm>e</targetForm>
        </over_capitalisation></foreign_word> <foreign_word foreign_language="Italiano"><over_capitalisation>
          <originalForm>CARATTERIALI</originalForm>

          <targetForm>caratteriali</targetForm>
        </over_capitalisation></foreign_word>) einfachlich <foreign_word foreign_language="Italiano"><over_capitalisation>
          <originalForm>SOPPERIRE</originalForm>

          <targetForm>sopperire</targetForm>
        </over_capitalisation></foreign_word>. Wenn du nicht mit diesen Personen sprichst, dann kannst du nicht ih<ambiguous>
